OL,3,CAurigny CEO defends Guernsey's airline
OL,4,Csaying it's faring better than others
OL,6,FNico Beizendehout admitted that 2024
OL,7,Fhad been a misery for the airline.
OL,9,FHowever, in response to public and
OL,10,Findustry concern, the packed audience
OL,11,Fwere told that Guernsey is actually
OL,12,Fdoing better than most of its peers.
OL,14,FThe audience were told that Guernsey
OL,15,Fis lucky to have Aurigny and that the
OL,16,Fisland is punching above its weight
OL,17,Fcompared to similar small airports.
