OL,6,FThis message which was not welcomed by
OL,7,Fsome in the audience, Barry Cash from
OL,8,FGuernsey Aviation Action Group said:
OL,9,F''There were no questions being asked
OL,10,Fabout why are we just relying on
OL,11,Flistening to the present incumbents
OL,12,Fwhen we should be standing back and
OL,13,Flooking objectively on what we really
OL,14,Fneed.'
